phishing story: joe wanted to get high end documents from a bank that can cripple a high end business. joe emails and calls some of the banks workers and manager support and asked if he could get the access code for it because he forgot it and that the business manager would be furious with him,the bank manager asks him for a 6 digit code that confirm that he was sent by the businesses manager.joe then calls the business saying that he was the manager of the bank and that he forgot the confirmaton code to get into the businesses information. the business gives him the code and he talks to the bank manager and gives him the 4 digit code that gets into the bank and takes the documents and posts them to everyone.
